Comprehensive Analysis of Improvements in Health-Related Quality of Life and 
Establishment of QALY Gains in a Government-Funded Bariatric Surgical Program 
with 5-Year Follow-up.

Chadwick C(1)(2), Burton PR(3)(4), Reilly J(3)(5), Playfair J(3), Laurie C(3), 
Shaw K(3)(4), Brown WA(3)(4).

Author information:
(1)Department of Surgery, Central Clinical School, Monash University, Alfred 
Health, Melbourne, VIC, Australia. Chiara.Chadwick@monash.edu.
(2)Oesophago-Gastric and Bariatric Unit, Alfred Health. Melbourne, Victoria, 
Australia. Chiara.Chadwick@monash.edu.
(3)Department of Surgery, Central Clinical School, Monash University, Alfred 
