Modeling the potential efficiency of a blood biomarker-based tool to guide 
pre-hospital thrombolytic therapy in stroke patients.

Parody-Rua E(1)(2), Bustamante A(3), Montaner J(4)(5), Rubio-Valera M(6)(7), 
