The Impact of 51 Risk Factors on Life Expectancy in Canada: Findings from a New 
Risk Prediction Model Based on Data from the Global Burden of Disease Study.

Kopec JA(1)(2), Sayre EC(2), Shams B(3), Li LC(2)(4), Xie H(2)(5), Feehan LM(4), 
Esdaile JM(2)(6).

Author information:
(1)School of Population and Public Health, University of British Columbia, 
Vancouver, BC V6T 1Z3, Canada.
(2)Arthritis Research Canada, Vancouver, BC V5Y 3P2, Canada.
(3)Fraser Health Authority, Surrey, BC V3T 0H1, Canada.
(4)Department of Physical Therapy, University of British Columbia, Vancouver, BC 
V6T 1Z3, Canada.
(5)Faculty of Health Sciences, Simon Fraser University, Burnaby, BC V5A 1S6, 
Canada.
(6)Department of Medicine, University of British Columbia, Vancouver, BC V5Z 
